name: OrderIso.preimage_Iic
initialProofState:
α : Type u_1
β : Type u_2
inst✝¹ : Preorder α
inst✝ : Preorder β
e : OrderIso α β
b : β
⊢ Eq (Set.preimage (⇑e) (Set.Iic b)) (Set.Iic (e.symm b))
decl:
@[simp]
theorem preimage_Iic (e : α ≃o β) (b : β) : e ⁻¹' Iic b = Iic (e.symm b) := by
  ext x
  simp [← e.le_iff_le]

name: OrderIso.image_Iic
initialProofState:
α : Type u_1
β : Type u_2
inst✝¹ : Preorder α
inst✝ : Preorder β
e : OrderIso α β
a : α
⊢ Eq (Set.image (⇑e) (Set.Iic a)) (Set.Iic (e a))
decl:
@[simp]
theorem image_Iic (e : α ≃o β) (a : α) : e '' Iic a = Iic (e a) := by
  rw [e.image_eq_preimage, e.symm.preimage_Iic, e.symm_symm]
